271
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,000
I believe she can resolve it.

272
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,440
It's just that the later we find her,

273
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:21,110
the more hardship she will endure.

274
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,160
Any hardship

275
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,240
is an opportunity for the Divine Lord.

276
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,300
What opportunity?

277
00:18:27,830 --> 00:18:29,760
The opportunity to kill Bai Jiusi.

278
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:17,720
The Heaven-Turning Seal has fallen
and the void has shattered,

279
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:20,440
yet there's not a single trace of Master.

280
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,680
I've summoned you all here today

281
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:26,290
to assist me in performing a formation

282
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,460
to search for Master.

283
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:31,790
We will do our best to assist you, Senior.

284
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,920
All disciples, protect me
as I perform the ritual.

285
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:35,720
-Yes!
-Yes!

286
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:22,840
It's late and chilly.

287
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:25,760
Where are you going
instead of resting inside?

288
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,110
Ruyue,

289
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,370
I'm talking to you.

290
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,610
What do you want?

291
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:42,880
Nothing.

292
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,410
I just want to talk with you.

293
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:48,720
What is there left to say between us?

294
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:55,000
Past events, what's right
and what's wrong...

295
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,970
There's a lot we can talk about.

296
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,210
With such a grand display,

297
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:23,300
Heavenly Lord Dacheng,
what do you want to discuss?

298
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:25,240
Four hundred and ten years ago,

299
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:27,370
I sealed your spiritual energy

300
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,490
and cast you back to heaven.

301
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,240
Do you still hate me?

302
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:34,350
What do you think?

303
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,880
After you regained your spiritual energy,

304
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:39,280
you pretended to marry me

305
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:41,330
and on our wedding day,

306
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:43,840
you stabbed my heart meridian
with the Hanlin Dagger,

307
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,500
suppressing me for a century.

308
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:49,920
Ruyue, isn't the century of suffering

309
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:54,270
enough to compensate for your
10 years of hardships in the mortal realm?

310
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,680
For pain, what matters

311
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:00,030
is intensity, not duration.

312
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:05,030
Fine. Then I'd like to know

313
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:07,360
just how deep your hatred is

314
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,150
that after sealing me,

315
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:11,110
you would plunder
magical artifacts and elixirs,

316
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:12,440
occupy immortal sects,

317
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,700
and act so recklessly,

318
00:22:13,830 --> 00:22:15,310
angering the heavens and the people.

319
00:22:15,310 --> 00:22:17,710
I've never seen the wrath
of heaven and men,

320
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:19,550
but there are plenty of immortals
who want to kill me.

321
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:20,240
You know,

322
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:22,050
I never wanted to kill you.

323
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,420
When I occupied Tianmu Peak,

324
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:25,220
all I wanted was an explanation.

325
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:28,720
You destroyed your own physical body

326
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,580
and your primordial spirit fled.

327
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:32,550
I never laid a hand on you.

328
00:22:32,550 --> 00:22:34,210
Even if you never attacked me,

329
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:36,990
you still deserve to die.

330
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:39,930
I deserve to die?

331
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:44,960
Do you think everything you've done
in the past

332
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:45,750
was right?

333
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:55,960
All effects arise from causes.

334
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,770
All retributions are born from karma.

335
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:02,960
The great drought in the world
was caused by the Drought Dragon.

336
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:05,670
But why don't you think about

337
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:09,450
how there are millions of
acres of land in the world,

338
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:11,030
but the Drought Dragon

339
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:12,890
only chose Mount Wuju as its lair?

340
00:23:14,510 --> 00:23:15,840
It's because Mount Wuju

341
00:23:16,660 --> 00:23:17,990
was its place of origin.

342
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:21,440
It was born in and cultivated there.

343
00:23:21,620 --> 00:23:25,960
But humans upended mountains and forests,
diverted water,

344
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:29,090
and slaughtered the creatures
on Mount Wuju.

345
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:30,900
Since then,

346
00:23:31,690 --> 00:23:35,420
the plants on Mount Wuju withered,
and the living beings suffered.

347
00:23:36,050 --> 00:23:37,450
It became a land of death.

348
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:42,270
The Drought Dragon had to leave this place

349
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:44,880
to find elsewhere to live.

350
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:00,870
You have a compassionate heart,

351
00:24:01,350 --> 00:24:03,880
killing the Drought Dragon
to save the world.

352
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,080
But if human lives are lives,

353
00:24:06,100 --> 00:24:08,370
aren't the lives of those creatures
on Mount Wuju

354
00:24:08,370 --> 00:24:09,520
also lives as well?

355
00:24:13,180 --> 00:24:15,810
Karma is a personal matter.

356
00:24:16,770 --> 00:24:19,550
Even the closest blood relatives
cannot bear it for another.

357
00:24:19,550 --> 00:24:20,590
The Drought Dragon cannot represent

358
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:23,250
the creatures that died
on Mount Wuju back then.

359
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:26,230
Those mortals who died
because of the drought

360
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:28,830
were not the ones who
caused harm back then.

361
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:29,920
You are a god.

362
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:32,920
You stand above the mortal world,
looking down on all living beings,

363
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:36,310
but you've never considered things
from their perspective.

364
00:24:36,310 --> 00:24:38,030
The causes were planted by others,

365
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:40,230
yet they have to bear the consequences.

366
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:42,560
This is not karma for them

367
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:44,630
but an undeserved disaster.

368
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:48,610
The way of heaven has its cycles.
Good and evil have their consequences.

369
00:24:48,610 --> 00:24:49,730
In ancient times,

370
00:24:50,190 --> 00:24:53,080
people ate raw meat, drank blood,
and walked naked.

371
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:57,850
Leizu invented silk
and Shennong identified herbs.

372
00:24:58,340 --> 00:25:01,730
Since then, people have had food to eat
and clothes to wear.

373
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,000
Since you speak of cause and effect,

374
00:25:05,390 --> 00:25:08,810
why do they only receive the good
and not bear the bad?

375
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:12,690
If you speak of heavenly retribution
and karmic consequences,

376
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:15,170
then let me discuss it with you.

377
00:25:20,990 --> 00:25:23,550
You say that causes and effects
are predetermined.

378
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,010
You and I were born as gods.

379
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:27,160
Are we also bound by this
cycle of cause and effect?

380
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:29,650
Meng Qi worked for Qichi Hall for decades.

381
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:32,020
Meng Chi dedicated his life to me.

382
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:34,730
Meng Changqin was even my disciple.

383
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:38,920
I received offerings from mortals.
That was the cause.

384
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:41,330
I slew the Drought Dragon
and protected the people.

385
00:25:41,330 --> 00:25:42,460
That was the effect.

386
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:46,420
You speak of the cycle of cause
and effect, and I follow this too.

387
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:49,380
Why are you right and I'm wrong?

388
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:50,520
You are a god.

389
00:25:51,510 --> 00:25:54,910
Your causes and effects shouldn't
be entangled with humans.

390
00:25:58,110 --> 00:25:59,640
You seem to have forgotten.

391
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:02,290
Eleven years ago,
at the foot of Yufan Mountain,

392
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:04,350
the real Li Qingyue had already died.

393
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:07,560
I entered her body
with my primordial spirit.

394
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:10,790
From that moment on,
I also became a mortal.

395
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:14,270
What about you, Heavenly Lord Dacheng?

396
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,130
Why are your causes and effects

397
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:19,530
still entangled with mine to this day?

398
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:24,240
I thought

399
00:26:26,130 --> 00:26:27,160
you knew.

400
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:32,480
Bai Jiusi,

401
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:37,240
have you ever tasted
the bitterness of the mortal realm?

402
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:40,560
You have never experienced
the helplessness of mortals.

403
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:43,180
You have no right to discuss this with me.

404
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:45,850
You sealed my power for
10 years back then.

405
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:49,710
Today, I want to make another
10-year pact with you

406
00:26:50,110 --> 00:26:52,040
to see who is right and who is wrong.

407
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:53,440
Do you dare?

408
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:56,450
Why wouldn't I dare?

409
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:01,840
Fine, but don't regret it later.

410
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:15,350
Senior!

411
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,280
Senior!

412
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:16,940
Senior!

413
00:27:16,970 --> 00:27:17,600
-Senior!
-Senior!

414
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:18,250
Senior.

415
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:25,000
Senior, have you found Master?

416
00:27:27,150 --> 00:27:30,550
The celestial phenomena have
changed, pointing to the east.

417
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:34,910
I tried to use the spirit escape technique
to rush to the east and investigate,

418
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:36,960
but I was blocked by a great flood.

419
00:27:36,990 --> 00:27:38,390
Blocked by a great flood?

420
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,010
What does this mean?

421
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,350
The air was filled with
bone-chilling mist.

422
00:27:48,130 --> 00:27:49,120
Master

423
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:51,480
must be in the water.

424
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:53,640
What should we do then?

425
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,380
Notify the dragon clans of the Four Seas.

426
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:58,440
Have them dispatch their naval forces

427
00:27:58,440 --> 00:27:59,700
and search for Master.

428
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:03,570
We absolutely can't let
Divine Lord Siling get the upper hand.

429
00:28:04,530 --> 00:28:07,800
Puyuan, notify all disciples
of Canglei Palace.

430
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:11,880
Head east and stop when
you encounter water.

431
00:28:12,740 --> 00:28:14,340
You must search thoroughly.

432
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,200
Don't miss a single corner.

433
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,600
Rest assured. I'll go
arrange this right away.

434
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,160
Elder!

435
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:29,750
Elder, Canglei Palace has acted.

436
00:28:31,310 --> 00:28:32,150
Where are they going?

437
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:33,350
They're heading east.

438
00:28:33,350 --> 00:28:35,610
The exact destination is still unknown.

439
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:38,000
Notify all disciples to head east.

440
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:41,540
We must find Master
before Canglei Palace does.

441
00:28:41,550 --> 00:28:42,030
Yes.

442
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:46,440
Master.

443
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:52,110
Qingyue was once my disciple.

444
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:55,310
She kept many things from me in the past,

445
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:58,170
but now,

446
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,920
I request to join the search for her.

447
00:29:08,290 --> 00:29:09,120
Very well.

448
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,940
Be careful in everything.

449
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,440
Yes, Master.

450
00:29:33,060 --> 00:29:34,700
[Simple Joy]

451
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,730
With your power sealed,

452
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:42,260
you must live here as a mortal
for 10 years.

453
00:29:43,650 --> 00:29:45,660
No matter what happens
during these 10 years,

454
00:29:45,660 --> 00:29:47,580
you must not use your power recklessly.

455
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:51,180
If you violate this restriction,
you will suffer consequences.

456
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:54,000
At the very least, your essence
and divine body will be damaged.

457
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:57,200
At worst, it'll be destroyed,
and you will never recover.

458
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,070
Okay.

459
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:05,780
I'll wait for you to show me the so-called
sufferings of the mortal realm.

460
00:30:11,410 --> 00:30:13,060
[Simple Joy]

461
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:17,750
So,

462
00:30:19,710 --> 00:30:21,310
am I considered a mortal now?

463
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:25,450
Where are these mortal
sufferings you speak of?

464
00:30:25,550 --> 00:30:28,110
Time is long. Experience it yourself.

465
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,140
Since I am a mortal,

466
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:32,790
I should have an identity.

467
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:36,360
If someone asks about our relationship,

468
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,010
how should I answer?

469
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:43,200
Why don't we

470
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:47,920
address each other as husband and wife?

471
00:30:48,770 --> 00:30:49,770
What do you think?

472
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:53,510
Whatever.

473
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,480
I don't understand mortals?

474
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:02,830
You're awake.

475
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:05,090
Come have some tea.

476
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,740
What are you doing?

477
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,030
I read a book last night

478
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:31,350
called "The Classic of Dwellings."

479
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,930
There's some truth in what it says.

480
00:32:34,790 --> 00:32:38,030
It says a dwelling's layout
is its body,

481
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:40,280
springs are its blood vessels,

482
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:44,110
land is its flesh,
and plants are its hair.

483
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:47,590
Houses are its clothes,
and gates are its hat.

484
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:50,640
If all these align, it's most auspicious.

485
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:53,110
Look at the

486
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:55,520
fengshui layout of this place now.

487
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:57,070
It really can't be compared

488
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:58,600
to the Qichi Hall I built you

489
00:32:59,160 --> 00:33:00,680
over 400 years ago

490
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:06,630
What? Do you want to build
another Qichi Hall?

491
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,110
Not exactly.

492
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:11,640
Just some minor renovations.

493
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:13,520
Come here.

494
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:14,880
I plan

495
00:33:15,590 --> 00:33:18,220
to add two more flower stands here

496
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:20,120
and grow some flowers and plants.

497
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,990
We'll raise some fish in this pond.

498
00:33:23,810 --> 00:33:25,140
The entire courtyard

499
00:33:25,190 --> 00:33:27,190
will be repainted and redecorated.

500
00:33:28,410 --> 00:33:29,740
Don't you like cooking?

501
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:32,240
I also plan to renovate

502
00:33:32,450 --> 00:33:33,710
this kitchen a little.

503
00:33:34,350 --> 00:33:35,350
What do you think?

504
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,250
Hey, Lord,

505
00:33:54,510 --> 00:33:57,400
what woman likes to spend
all her time in the kitchen?

506
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:59,350
If you really want to please your wife,

507
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:00,750
you should cook with her,

508
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:02,960
not just renovate a kitchen for her.

509
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,460
Let's pack up everything.

510
00:34:35,070 --> 00:34:35,929
We're leaving.

511
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:36,670
Come down.

512
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,590
Sir.

513
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,250
It's already finished?

514
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:42,000
Lord, the remaining work

515
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,250
can be finished tomorrow,

516
00:34:43,250 --> 00:34:44,850
so we'll head back for today.

517
00:34:45,550 --> 00:34:46,050
Be careful.

518
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:46,590
Let's go.

519
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:48,489
Let's go.

520
00:35:07,190 --> 00:35:08,790
You must be the new neighbor.

521
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:13,280
I'm Lin Fan. I live next door.

522
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,960
My wife just made some pastries.

523
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,560
I brought some for you to try.

524
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:20,230
Thank you,

525
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,900
but that's not necessary.

526
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:26,010
Don't be so polite with me.

527
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:26,920
Look how hungry you are.

528
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:27,400
Here.

529
00:35:30,810 --> 00:35:31,360
Hungry?

530
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,480
We're neighbors now.

531
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,970
May I ask your name?

532
00:35:40,110 --> 00:35:40,830
Bai Jiusi.

533
00:35:41,730 --> 00:35:42,670
Bai Jiusi?

534
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:45,070
I'll leave these here for you.

535
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:45,550
No need.

536
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:49,530
Remember to eat them, Bai.

537
00:35:50,490 --> 00:35:51,150
Goodbye.

538
00:35:54,890 --> 00:35:56,090
Remember to eat them!

539
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:15,960
You're back.

540
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,330
What are you cooking today?

541
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,040
It smells delicious.

542
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:21,760
Let me help you.

